# Summary
The Settings page in Amplitude provides organization-wide and personal configuration options, accessible via the settings icon. While all users can view settings, only admins and managers can modify them. The page includes organization information, user management, usage reports, notification preferences, SSO configuration, and personal profile settings including Slack integration options.

